27T14:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/220905_70fe99a7019a0beae15de074255ce94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F220905_70fe99a7019a0beae15de074255ce94c.jpg&h=c5907fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/220922_b3e0983c8cc52b9e3d0b3ea82d3dd564.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F220922_b3e0983c8cc52b9e3d0b3ea82d3dd564.jpg&h=31cfe3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/220932_e47f059c9ef5f8b994e62a82a3253158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F220932_e47f059c9ef5f8b994e62a82a3253158.jpg&h=a4d491ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/221138_95244915a9ac4cfe3b7118980e189af1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F221138_95244915a9ac4cfe3b7118980e189af1.jpg&h=696583cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本一件uniqlo hoodie 其實好夠玩<br />\n要一件套頭果啲，唔好買拉鏈，個形靚啲<br />\n覺得悶可以買啲有logo既，nike addi gap果啲<br />\n再唔夠可以自己買多年外套做layer<br />\n棒球褸，牛仔褸，ma1 都可以。<br />\n褲就jogger,牛仔褲棉褲，隨便咩都得<br />\n色都係隨便你，你吹到要粉紅，紫色都okay<br />\n當然黑白灰軍綠navy依啲係最正路<br />\n鞋就波鞋，唔好行山鞋就可以<br />\n你想潮啲（or so call 潮童啲？idk)<br />\n可以買superstar,sockdart,nmd果啲<br />\n得閒可以睇下kayne點著衫<br />\n基本上佢點樣尻著都好睇<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/222644_37888dcb9d6902c7ebbc997123dbad90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F222644_37888dcb9d6902c7ebbc997123dbad90.jpg&h=fd2c1390&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/222750_426e5ac9f76a56331a462f4a67aef29e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F222750_426e5ac9f76a56331a462f4a67aef29e.jpg&h=129e0b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n查實岩身最緊要，點叫岩身就要交學費<br />\n自己去試多啲衫，因為睇身型，<br />\n有時少少oversize先好睇<br />\n無公式依樣野"},{"pid":"c5444297e73ca3da0415544b034d0738e6edf13e","tid":6741,"uid":7737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"留名學野脫毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3853755a268dc93b91bd54c698f0b6b29c42ad","tid":6741,"uid":21184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>衛衣<br />\n順次序<br />\n衫褲鞋<br />\n<br />\n灰黑黑<br />\n白黑黑<br />\n黑黑白<br />\n黑黑黑（鞋最好搭少少其他色）<br />\n<br />\n唔太凍可以試t-shirt搭外套</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得黑白灰就咪教人襯啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都無講佢條褲咩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁正路都買呢啲色啦 都講明左係經典"},{"pid":"e3938202f6f701f94a58ee5ea0ac3e454ddb0a75","tid":6741,"uid":21184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/220905_70fe99a7019a0beae15de074255ce94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F220905_70fe99a7019a0beae15de074255ce94c.jpg&h=b7be598f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/220922_b3e0983c8cc52b9e3d0b3ea82d3dd564.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F220922_b3e0983c8cc52b9e3d0b3ea82d3dd564.jpg&h=43e1c5a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/220932_e47f059c9ef5f8b994e62a82a3253158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F220932_e47f059c9ef5f8b994e62a82a3253158.jpg&h=d6fab7ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http: